parameters: \n<Valam soldier A>"Damn it...! We're going to be overrun at this rate!!"

\n<Valam soldier C>"--Fall back!! It's hopeless here! Retreat to the
castle--!!"
\n<Begieade>"...Did they escape. It's only a matter of time now."

\n<Begieade>"Hey, monsters. There's no need to rampage so wildly. You
all wait here."

\n<Begieade>"Tch... Difficult to handle. This body is indeed
inconvenient... Well, it doesn't matter if I kill a few too
many."

\n<Begieade>"Nfufu... What are you saying? This is something you
yourself desire. Why should I stop?"
\n<Ameria>"No... I don't wish for this kind of thing...!"

\n<Begieade>"You're wrong. You know the truth, don't you...? Isn't that
right? That's right, Ameria."
\n<Begieade>"Nfufu... Don't make such a sad face."
\n<Begieade>"I'm on your side. So relax and entrust yourself to me."

\n<Ameria>"I don't wish for this! If Lyric is with me... If Lyric is
by my side, that's all I need...!"

\n<Begieade>"No, you're mistaken. Your dream of becoming a splendid
healer. That's everything, and this is the story that was
desired."
\n<Ameria>"It's Lyric who will fulfill my wish! Not someone like you!"

\n<Ameria>"That's right! I'll be fine! Because Lyric will definitely
come to save me!"

\n<Begieade>"Nfufu... As if anyone will come to save you. You saw it
earlier. That pitiful figure trembling in fear, unable to
even understand herself."

\n<Begieade>"An empty shell. A mere doll who can't do anything alone. Do
you really think she can come here to save you?"

\n<Ameria>"When I was suffering and lonely...! Even when I was being
selfish...! She was always there by my side...!"
\n<Ameria>"So she will definitely...! Definitely come to save me!"
\n<Begieade>"...Ridiculous. If only words could do anything--"

\n<Ameria>"She's not empty! She's not just a doll! She's kinder and
stronger than anyone else! She's my precious friend!"
\n<Ameria>"Lyric will come to save me! She will always be by my side!"
\n<Ameria>"So I absolutely won't lose to someone like you!!"
\n<Begieade>"What do you mean... You were certainly dead!"
\n<Roselitte>"Yes, at that time, I certainly lost my life. --But..."
Roselitte looked at Ameria and smiled.

\n<Roselitte>"She is kinder and stronger than anyone else... She's not
just a doll. She's our precious friend."
\n<Roselitte>"And I will become the sword that carves the path for her."

\n<Lyric>"What was that introduction just now? It's completely
different from what we discussed earlier. I was confused
about when to make my entrance."

\n<Roselitte>"...I would never want to say something so embarrassing,
even in death."

\n<Lyric>"Eh? 'I've danced back from hell, baby!' followed by 'I
didn't just look at the afterlife for nothing!' and then my
entrance, ta-da! ...It's cool, right?"

\n<Begieade>"You seem pretty relaxed. Just a while ago you were all
scared."

\n<Lyric>"Shut up, idiot. I don't want to hear that from you right
now."

\n<Lyric>"Your voice is trembling quite a bit as you look at me.
Could it be that you're scared of me?"

\n<Roselitte>"...Your reasons for using Lyric, the goal of fulfilling
Ameria's wish, and the miracle of my presence here"

\n<Roselitte>"If by chance, this answer is correct. Then I can explain
all of it. --Answer my question."

\n<??>"--I'm delighted. So delighted, Elador. This is what they
call a thrilling sensation. Ah, ah... I'm so moved I could
almost throw up..."
\n<??>"I never thought you would break the seal yourself!"
\n<??>"Ah, wonderful! Yes! It's you! I wanted you as you are now!"

\n<??>"Was it you who awakened it, Roselitte? Let me thank you!
You've done well for my sake!"

\n<??>"Ah, I want it! I want it! I want it! Elador! I want you!
--And...!"

\n<??>"Give it back give it back give it back give it back give it
back give it back give it back give it back!! That's mine!
My power! It is me!"

\n<??>"I will take that power back! Elador! And Roselitte! You
won't get a second chance!"

\n<Lyric>"Listen. It might be dark and scary there. But my voice will
surely reach you."
\n<Lyric>"Trust in my voice. I will definitely rescue you."

\n<Roselitte>"...It's okay. I was able to stand up because of Lyric's
voice."

\n<Roselitte>"I will definitely save you. So just hang in there a little
longer."

\n<??>"It's useless to say anything... Your voices won't reach
Ameria!"
\n<??>"Ah, I have always! Always been waiting for this moment!"

\n<??>"Let me thank you, Roselitte! Thanks to you, I can become
one! As a reward, I'll invite you into the vortex of
desire!"

\n<??>"And... Elador! Ahh! Once more! Like that time! Take my
hand! Then we can surpass even the gods!"

\n<??>"That power! The supreme nourishment that breeds lust! Ahh!
It's all, all, all mine!!"

\n<Roselitte>"...Lyric. If my voice reaches you, there's no way it won't
reach Ameria."

\n<Roselitte>"I will clear the path. I will brush away the sparks that
fall upon us. You just need to keep moving forward."

\n<Roselitte>"You are a wonderful girl who can make wishes come true.
Because you are Lyric."
\n<Roselitte>"--Come on, let's go! I entrust Ameria to you!"

\n<Lyric>"...Yeah. Let's go together! This time for sure... we'll
save her!"
\n<The gluttonous grimoire>"Guh...! What on earth are you thinking!? "
\n<The gluttonous grimoire>"Ku, don't come any closer! Stay away!!"
\n<Lyric>"Whoa!? Don't kick Ameria away, you idiot!"
Roselitte and Lyric have pinned down Ameria!
\n<The gluttonous grimoire>"Wha... What are you doing, Elador! Let go!!"

\n<Lyric>"--Ameria! You don't need the magic book anymore! I'm here
for you! I'll be your support!"

\n<Lyric>"I want to be with you too! I'll stay by your side forever!
I'll always protect you!"
